apper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/STM\" title=\"STMicroelectronics N.V.\">STM</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/STMEF\" title=\"STMicroelectronics N.V.\">OTCPK:STMEF</a>) is one of the leading semiconductor manufacturers in the world. After strong growth in FY 2021 and FY 2022, STM\u2019s growth decelerated in FY 2023. Since then, the company has faced significant challenges in FY2024, with plunging</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547238585/image_1547238585.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742946-stmicroelectronics-stock-worst-has-been-priced-in-initiating-with-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 10:17:30"}, {"id": "4742945", "title": "IGM: I Don't See The Point", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533019596/image_1533019596.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Two businesspeople looking at desktop computer monitor and discussing work at desk\" data-id=\"1533019596\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533019596/image_1533019596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533019596/image_1533019596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533019596/image_1533019596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533019596/image_1533019596.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533019596/image_1533019596.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533019596/image_1533019596.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533019596/image_1533019596.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/