39.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Shutthiphong Chandaeng</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>At my core, I am a value investor. But this doesn't mean that I always look for the cheapest opportunities. While I do prioritize the price that I am paying for companies above most anything else, I do also acknowledge that some</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742942-esquire-financial-holdings-precipice-of-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 09:20:31"}, {"id": "4742940", "title": "POET Technologies: High Risk, High Reward In The AI Data Center Revolution", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210742344/image_1210742344.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Technology Researching\" data-id=\"1210742344\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8256px\" height=\"5504px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210